# PR hygiene (quality)

- Prefer small, reviewable diffs; avoid unrelated refactors.
- If behavior or plot output changes, note how it was verified (`python3 example_scientific_plot.py`).
- Do not commit secrets or expand `environment.json` without a clear need.
- Use `[review]` in the agent title when the run’s job is critique rather than implementation.
- For implement/domain runs, open or update a PR with a concise summary of category + outcome.
